<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. مُصَلِّ بِلا قُرْآنِهِ الْمُتَأَكِّدِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>قُنُوطُ الْفَتَى مِنْ رَحْمَةِ اللهِ ثُمَّ قُلْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِسَاءَةً ظَنِّ بِالإِلَهِ الْمُوَحَّدِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَأَمْنٌ لِمَكْرِ اللهِ ثُمَّ قَطِيعَةٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>لِذِي رَحِمٍ وَالْكِبْرُ وَالْخُيَلا اعْدُدِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>كَذَا كَذِبٌ إِنْ كَانَ يَرْمِي بِفِتْنَةٍ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أَوْ الْمُفْتَرِي يَوْمًا عَلَى الْمُصْطَفَى أَحْمَدِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>قِيَادَةُ دَيُّوثٍ نِكَاحٌ مُحَلِّلٍ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَهِجْرَةُ عَدْلٍ مُسْلِمٍ وَمُوَحِّدِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَتَرْكُ لِحَجٍ مُسْتَطِيعًا وَمَنْعُهُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>زَكَاةً وَحُكْمُ الْحَاكِمِ الْمُتَقَلِّدِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بِحَقِّ لِخَلْقِ وَارْتِشَاهُ وَفِطْرُهُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>بِلا عُذْرِهِ فِي صَوْمِ شَهْرِ التَّعَبُّدِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَقَوْلٌ بِلا عِلْمٍ عَلَى اللهِ رَبِّنَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَسَبٌّ لأَصْحَابِ النَّبِي مُحَمَّدِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>مُصِرٌّ عَلَى الْعِصْيَانِ تَرْكُ تَنَزُّهٍ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>مِنَ الْبُولِ فِي نَصِّ الْحَدِيثِ الْمُسَدَّدِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَإِتْيَانُ مَنْ حَاضَتْ بِفَرْجٍ وَنَشْزُهَا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>عَلَى زَوْجِهَا مِنْ غَيْرِ عُذْرٍ مُهَمَّدِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَإِلْحَاقُهَا بِالزَّوْجِ مَنْ حَمَلَتْهُ مِنْ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>سِوَاهُ وَكِتْمَانُ الْعُلُومِ لِمُجْتَدِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>